A search results page can't be a site page. It has to be a search result system page. Unfortunately there isnt any good way to stage a system page to test it. 

I have a weird work around I've used in the past. By changing the template based on a query parameter

 {% if request.query_dict.hsDebug != true %}
 {% include './template-v2.html' %}
 {% else %}
 {% include './template-v1.html' %}
 {% endif %}
